### Measurement Results - Get all with pagination
GET http://localhost:5202/api/MeasurementResults?pageNumber=1&pageSize=10
Accept: application/json

###

### Measurement Results - Get by id
GET http://localhost:5202/api/MeasurementResults/REPLACE_WITH_RESULT_ID
Accept: application/json

###

### Measurement Results - Create
POST http://localhost:5202/api/MeasurementResults
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "partName": "Rear Cover",
  "serialNumber": "SN-10001",
  "measurementType": "Length",
  "measuredValue": 125.4,
  "unit": "mm",
  "lowerLimit": 120.0,
  "upperLimit": 130.0,
  "status": "PASS",
  "measuredBy": "Operator A",
  "measuredAt": "2026-03-20T08:30:00Z",
  "notes": "Initial sample result"
}

###

### Measurement Results - Update
PUT http://localhost:5202/api/MeasurementResults/REPLACE_WITH_RESULT_ID
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "partName": "Rear Cover",
  "serialNumber": "SN-10001",
  "measurementType": "Length",
  "measuredValue": 118.9,
  "unit": "mm",
  "lowerLimit": 120.0,
  "upperLimit": 130.0,
  "status": "FAIL",
  "measuredBy": "Operator B",
  "measuredAt": "2026-03-20T09:15:00Z",
  "notes": "Updated after recheck"
}

###

### Measurement Results - Delete
DELETE http://localhost:5202/api/MeasurementResults/REPLACE_WITH_RESULT_ID